snippet.title: Russian Subway Dogs - Debut Trailer!
snippet.description:
OUT NOW ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/762610/Russian_Subway_Dogs/
A fast-paced arcade game inspired by the real-life stray dogs who ride the Moscow Metro. From the creators of They Bleed Pixels.

Find out more at www.spookysquid.com/rsd
